metadata.name: サイバーパンクカフェ
metadata.description:
#1 of the ThreeSixtyFive collection.

サイバーパンクカフェ (or "Cyberpunk Cafe" in Japanese) explores the social dynamics of a potential dystopian future in a distinct Japanese painting style, staged in a commercial poster format to give it a more dramatic and personable effect. 

Art by GANSY.
